<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>杂文 on 黄石的时空回环</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/tags/%E6%9D%82%E6%96%87/</link><description>Recent content in 杂文 on 黄石的时空回环</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© Copyright Ye Zhiling</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Jun 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yzlnew.com/tags/%E6%9D%82%E6%96%87/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>小猫咪的一年</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2022/06/cat-one-year/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jun 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2022/06/cat-one-year/</guid><description>&lt;p>去年今天，刚准备从干了两年的前司跳槽。临近傍晚的时候公司前台在群里发消息说，公司跑进来一只小猫，被抓进快递箱了。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>是不是应该重新开始写作了？</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2021/02/back-to-writing/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Feb 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2021/02/back-to-writing/</guid><description>&lt;p>小的时候对成人世界没有太多幻想，升学、读书、保研、打工挣钱，按部就班、四平八稳。
也渐渐意识到要混进更上一层，卷、世故、用各种信息差优势「剥削」别人，是不可避免的。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>牙的冒险</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2020/11/adventure-of-teeth/</link><pubDate>Wed, 25 Nov 2020 22:32:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2020/11/adventure-of-teeth/</guid><description>&lt;p>为庆祝赛博朋克 2077 的上线，我将装上第一颗人工义🦷。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>隐秘的渴望</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2020/06/the-bad-kids/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jun 2020 10:40:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2020/06/the-bad-kids/</guid><description>&lt;p>写这篇文章的时候我正听着原声带，里面有不少光怪陆离的氛围音乐，非常适合不想睡的晚上一个人听。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>被偷走的 2020</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2020/03/ncov-2019/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2020 13:44:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2020/03/ncov-2019/</guid><description>&lt;p>这篇文章很久之前就打算写了，看了下时间戳是 3 月 1 号。现在已经马上就要四月份了。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Cheer 20</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/12/cheer20/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2019 01:16:50 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/12/cheer20/</guid><description>&lt;p>本来是平凡的一天。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>不死鸟之死</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/12/immortal-bird/</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2019 01:36:50 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/12/immortal-bird/</guid><description>&lt;p>很久以前，绿洲里有一只不死鸟。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hey Jude</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/10/hey-jude/</link><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2019 19:44:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/10/hey-jude/</guid><description>&lt;p>纽约时报说，一个人的音乐品味的形成，最重要的是青少年时期，也就是 13-16 岁。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>开始工作的新开始</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/09/new-start/</link><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2019 11:03:43 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/09/new-start/</guid><description>&lt;p>好久没有更新博客了，最近在干啥呢。那最主要还是毕业了，去上班了。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>当我 27</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/07/when-i-am-27/</link><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2019 22:47:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/07/when-i-am-27/</guid><description>&lt;p>脑海中有时想起陈绮贞的「after 17」。第一次听到这首歌的时候，我真的就只有 17 岁。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>终章，新生</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/06/end-and-beginning/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2019 13:24:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/06/end-and-beginning/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="终章">终章&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>学生生涯逐渐进入尾声。有一种莫名的感觉萦绕着我。不是交完论文之后的空虚，不是对于
未知生活的无限憧憬。而是单纯的是什么都没有。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>我的昨天</title><link>https://yzlnew.com/2019/02/my-stories-1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Feb 2019 15:59:51 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yzlnew.com/2019/02/my-stories-1/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="情绪与故事">情绪与故事&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>之前看到一篇公众号文章里，说到作者学生时代大雪「落在身上」，感受到那种「情绪」，
发现自己可以做这一行。我想想我好像也有。不过我们这里就不是东北的雪，是下雨。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>